headline: Nasdaq Announces End-of-Month Open Short Interest Positions in Nasdaq Stocks as of Settlement Date January 31, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, Feb. 11, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- At the end of the settlement date of January 31, 2025, short interest in 3,109 Nasdaq Global MarketSM securities totaled 12,170,722,591 shares compared with 12,402,417,655 shares in 3,099 Global Market issues reported for the prior settlement date of January 15, 2025. The mid-January short interest represents 2.69 days compared with 2.56 days for the prior reporting period. Short interest in 1,621 securities on The Nasdaq Capital MarketSM totaled 2,410
